title: Don'T Stop Keep Going!!!! wit Money Bag Mafia, Karlous Miller, Chico Bean & DCYoungFly | Ep. 259
itunes:title: Don'T Stop Keep Going!!!! wit Money Bag Mafia, Karlous Miller, Chico Bean & DCYoungFly | Ep. 259
description:
On this hilarious episode, Money Bag Mafia comes through the trap to bring his comedy to people. Here how Money Bag grew up with DC Young Fly and the evolution of the their stand up comedy career. Plus, the crew examines the stand-up comedy life and Karlous drops some tips about how to stay out of the "Suck Box." Plus the crew looks at some of Money Bag's funniest comedy skits and the crew talks about that crazy lady that threw that puppy! This is the coldest podcast!
